Actress Uche Ogbodo has encouraged single ladies not to give up on love. The mother of two, who recently confirmed that she’s happily remarried to her younger lover and baby daddy, Bobby Marris advised single ladies to improve on themselves while waiting to be found by their rightful partners.   Iyabo Ojo lauds daughter for acquiring new Benz     No justification for hitting a woman – Obi Cubana     Obi Cubana instructs youths on selflessness   Ogbodo insisted good men still abound as she urged the single ladies to wait patiently and theirs would find them. “Ladies Be Patient, there are still Good Men Out there, your own will find you. Work On being the best version of yourself first,” she wrote.